- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper extensively uses machine learning techniques for acoustic modeling. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses artificial intelligence techniques for speech recognition. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses a biologically inspired CNN architecture for acoustic modeling.
